Arena Breakout is a tactical shooter with hardcore gameplay. The game can be described as a mobile version of Escape from Tarkov, as it recreates almost all the mechanics of this popular looter-shooter. At any point during a match, you can die and lose absolutely everything. Therefore, the more valuable items you have with you, the higher the stakes. Before heading out, you can arm yourself, put on a helmet and body armor, and grab ammunition, medkits, and keys. Without at least minimal equipment, even bots can kill you, but you shouldn’t take too much either, as you’ll need to leave room in your bags for future loot. Once you’re on the map, to win, you’ll need to get to the evacuation point, which will transport you to the safe house. Along the way, you’ll search containers and fight other players, and after defeating them, see what interesting items are in their bags and take them for yourself. If you want to bring home something valuable from each raid, you should think about buying Arena Breakout Top Up and get a bulletproof protected container with 4 slots or a composite safe with 6 slots. Items you place in these containers won’t be lost, even if your character gets killed.

The first matches allow newcomers to get accustomed, as more bots than live players spawn on the maps. Bots not only stand still for a couple of seconds before they start shooting, but they are also poorly equipped and die with one or two shots. You will be able to kill them easily and quickly climb the ranks, after which you will encounter well-equipped live players more and more often. In addition, access to new maps with more valuable loot will open up, and going there without good equipment makes no sense, as you’ll be killed instantly. If you don’t feel like farming, we suggest buying Arena Breakout Top Up and getting sets with armor and weapons. With these, your chances of winning will increase, as you will be much harder to kill.

If you enjoy the game and spend almost every day on the streets of Camona, it makes sense to buy Arena Breakout subscription. With it, you will receive koens and other useful items on your account. Every player has moments when luck isn’t on their side and they lose, and that’s when the bonuses come in handy for resupplying and heading back into battle.

On FunPay, purchasing top up for mobile games is safe and effortless. Placing an order takes less than a minute, and you can pay for goods using one of many available methods. Once the funds reach the site, the security system will reserve them and notify the seller of the new order. Only after you verify the receipt of the goods and confirm the order completion, the money will be transferred to the seller.

How to Top Up Arena Breakout

  1. Choose an offer.
  2. Contact the seller.
  3. Pay for the order.
  4. Verify the receipt of the goods.
  5. Confirm order completion.

For Sellers

In full-loot games, players often lose everything, and top up helps not only retain some items but also resupply at the market and head into the next match prepared. Some players face difficulties with payments, and that’s where you can help them by adding funds to the game. We suggest registering, selling Arena Breakout Top Up, and make a profit on the price difference.
